<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="storm-n">storm <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /stɔːm/    美 /stɔːrm/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>风暴；暴风雨：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sun returns after every storm.
阳光总在风雨后。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>be caught in a storm
遇上暴风雨</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>brain storm</strong>
头脑风暴</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>stormy /'stɔːmi/ adj   </p></div>